  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NIGHT OF THE WENDIGO</strong> is a Virtual Reality horror experience in which a peaceful day of hiking becomes a night of survival! The game is an intuitive, addictive VR experience that is best enjoyed by taking turns with friends. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/5e4973f7d20f72886452ad2edab6ffcc.poster.avif?t=1747955552\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/5e4973f7d20f72886452ad2edab6ffcc.webm?t=1747955552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/5e4973f7d20f72886452ad2edab6ffcc.mp4?t=1747955552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player must survive the night using their rechargeable flashlight to fend against forest animals such as deer, wolves, and the legendary Wendigo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/24d3da4dc3c25dc7c870431597ae0b46.poster.avif?t=1747955552\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/24d3da4dc3c25dc7c870431597ae0b46.webm?t=1747955552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/24d3da4dc3c25dc7c870431597ae0b46.mp4?t=1747955552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A thrilling Survival Mode can be unlocked where the player is armed with a pump-action shotgun after playing through the main Story Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/45f70418b4ab41a2478ab2ff4d593fe6.poster.avif?t=1747955552\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/45f70418b4ab41a2478ab2ff4d593fe6.webm?t=1747955552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/45f70418b4ab41a2478ab2ff4d593fe6.mp4?t=1747955552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview:</strong><br>- 10-20 minute Story Mode<br>- Endless Survival Mode!<br>- Intuitive, easy-to-understand gameplay<br>- Scary, scripted sequences and potential threats from any direction<br>- Roomscale experience. No need to worry about motion sickness!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NIGHT OF THE WENDIGO</strong> is a Virtual Reality horror experience in which a peaceful day of hiking becomes a night of survival! The game is an intuitive, addictive VR experience that is best enjoyed by taking turns with friends. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/5e4973f7d20f72886452ad2edab6ffcc.poster.avif?t=1747955552\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/5e4973f7d20f72886452ad2edab6ffcc.webm?t=1747955552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/5e4973f7d20f72886452ad2edab6ffcc.mp4?t=1747955552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player must survive the night using their rechargeable flashlight to fend against forest animals such as deer, wolves, and the legendary Wendigo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/24d3da4dc3c25dc7c870431597ae0b46.poster.avif?t=1747955552\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/24d3da4dc3c25dc7c870431597ae0b46.webm?t=1747955552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/24d3da4dc3c25dc7c870431597ae0b46.mp4?t=1747955552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A thrilling Survival Mode can be unlocked where the player is armed with a pump-action shotgun after playing through the main Story Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/45f70418b4ab41a2478ab2ff4d593fe6.poster.avif?t=1747955552\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/45f70418b4ab41a2478ab2ff4d593fe6.webm?t=1747955552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440790/extras/45f70418b4ab41a2478ab2ff4d593fe6.mp4?t=1747955552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview:</strong><br>- 10-20 minute Story Mode<br>- Endless Survival Mode!<br>- Intuitive, easy-to-understand gameplay<br>- Scary, scripted sequences and potential threats from any direction<br>- Roomscale experience. No need to worry about motion sickness!</p>",
